task.summary: Some tests for lexer are created
The first version of Lexer is created
The first version of Lexer is revised
The first version of CUP specification is done.
The CUP specification has been successfully compiled for the first time.
The parser and the lexer passed some easy tests made by myself.
The parser compile process automated using Apache Ant.
All 8 tests passed.(manually judged) Phase 1 Complete. No Bonus work has been done.
The UglyPrinter (which could make a piece of refined code into a terrible mess) function implemented. Changes are made to the AST, the parser and the lexer.
The first version of GUI implemented.
Resolved the reduplication of struct/union definition.
The robustness of Lexer, Parser and Pretty Printer is greatly Enhanced. Completed some portion of Phase 2 : Semantic Check.
Phase 2 : Now Passed some trivial tests.
Major bug fix in the type system.
Most known bugs of Phase 2 are fixed. New feature : 增加了可以统计报警次数的报警按钮！
A huge update for the basic framework of Phase 2.
The Interpreter passed all the tests of last year.
